  "prompt": "Which is best mobile under 15000?",
  "response": "As of October 2023, there are several great mobile smartphones available under \u20b915,000 in India. Here are some of the best options that you might consider:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 50**:\n   - Display: 6.6-inch FHD+ display\n   - Processor: MediaTek Helio G96\n   - RAM/Storage: Up to 6GB RAM and 128GB storage\n   - Camera: 50 MP triple camera, 16 MP front\n   - Battery: 5000 mAh\n\n2. **Xiaomi Redmi Note 11**:\n   - Display: 6.43-inch FHD+ AMOLED display\n   - Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 680\n   - RAM/Storage: Up to 6GB RAM and 128GB storage\n   - Camera: 50 MP quad-camera setup, 13 MP front\n   - Battery: 5000 mAh\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M32**:\n   - Display: 6.4-inch FHD+ Super AMOLED\n   - Processor: MediaTek Helio G80\n   - RAM/Storage: Up to 6GB RAM and 128GB storage\n   - Camera: 64 MP quad-camera, 20 MP front\n   - Battery: 6000 mAh\n\n4. **Poco M4 Pro**:\n   - Display: 6.43-inch FHD+ AMOLED display\n   - Processor: MediaTek Dimensity 810\n   - RAM/Storage: Up to 6GB RAM and 128GB storage\n   - Camera: 64 MP dual-camera, 16 MP front\n   - Battery: 5000 mAh\n\n5. **Moto G71**:\n   - Display: 6.4-inch FHD+ OLED display\n   - Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 695\n   - RAM/Storage: 6GB RAM and 128GB storage\n   - Camera: 50 MP triple-camera, 16 MP front\n   - Battery: 5000 mAh\n\nMake sure to check for any ongoing deals or discounts, as well as availability in your region. Additionally, your choice may depend on specific features like camera quality, battery life, or brand preference.",
